short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds Nux Taku to YouTube thumbnails and replaces singular first-person pronouns with plural equivalents in titles

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Someone tweeted 'Browser extensions that takes every Youtube video starting with "I", replaces it with "we", and adds Nux Taku in the thumbnail', so I decided to make it.

This extension might have bugs so please report them on GitHub if you find them! Click the support website to report them.
